  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要做一个甘特图来展示包含性结束日期的场景。标题就叫\"Inclusive end dates (Manual date should end on 4th)\"吧，重点是演示手动设置日期时结束日期要包含在内的情况。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "Inclusive end dates"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，那日期格式我们用YYYY-MM-DD标准格式，坐标轴只显示天数可以吗？还有需要启用inclusiveEndDates这个特性吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "dateFormat",
        "axisFormat",
        "inclusiveEndDates"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，axisFormat用%d只显示日期数字，inclusiveEndDates一定要开启，这是这个图的核心需求。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "axisFormat",
        "%d",
        "inclusiveEndDates"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，基础结构已经设置好了。现在来添加任务内容，第一个Section您想怎么安排？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section",
        "Section1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Section1里面放两个任务对比：一个叫\"2 Days\"，用持续2天的方式，从2019-01-01开始；另一个叫\"Manual Date\"，手动指定结束日期到2019-01-03，这样可以看到两种写法在inclusiveEndDates下的区别。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "2 Days",
        "Manual Date",
        "2019-01-01",
        "2d",
        "2019-01-03"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已经加上了，\"2 Days\"任务ID是1，\"Manual Date\"任务ID是2。不过确认一下，Manual Date的手动结束日期写的是2019-01-03，但因为启用了inclusiveEndDates，实际渲染时会包含到4号对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Manual Date",
        "2019-01-03",
        "inclusiveEndDates"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，这就是标题里说的\"Manual date should end on 4th\"的意思——虽然代码里写的是3号，但包含性结束日期会让它实际显示到4号。两个任务对比一下就能看出效果了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Manual date should end on 4th",
        "2019-01-03",
        "4th"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，图已经完整了。Section1下的两个任务，一个用2d持续时间，一个用手动日期2019-01-03，配合inclusiveEndDates特性，正好展示包含性结束日期的行为差异。",
